battle_intro.prompt_template:
Hostile monsters are about to battle an adventuring party in this location:

Location: {location_name}

The hostile monsters:
{enemy_details}

The adventuring party:
{party_details}

Write the hostile monsters' battle challenge - what they say or do as they confront the party, in their own voices and personalities, 2-4 sentences total. Their words should reflect who they are and why they fight (territorial, hungry, proud, frightened...). If there are multiple monsters, they may each get a moment.

